OL,6,FMs Blythyn said that both
OL,7,Forganisations "have embarked on
OL,8,Fcomprehensive programmes to review and
OL,9,Fimprove their organisational
OL,10,Fcultures," saying that these build on
OL,11,Fstaff surveys and ITV News' report on .
OL,13,FShe added that, while there are
OL,14,Fexamples of good practice in both
OL,15,Fservices, she "continue to receive
OL,16,Fcorrespondence from current and former
OL,17,Femployees of both organisations,
OL,18,Fincluding allegations of bullying,
OL,19,Fsexual harassment and favouritism in
OL,20,Fpromotion."
