OL,6,FMs Blythyn continued: "The public need
OL,7,Fto be re-assured about the culture and
OL,8,Frelated management practices in our
OL,9,Ffire and rescue services and staff
OL,10,Fneed to be assured they have a safe
OL,11,Fand effective means to share their
OL,12,Fexperiences ` good and bad ` within
OL,13,Ftheir organisation."
OL,15,FBoth and have agreed to carry out an
OL,16,Findependent review, with Ms Blythyn
OL,17,Fsaying she would expect them to
OL,18,Fpublish a report no later than autumn
OL,19,Fthis year.
