OL,6,FRoger Thomas, chief fire officer of
OL,7,Fsaid: "We welcome Welsh Government's
OL,8,Fdecision to accept our proposal to
OL,9,Freview how we are progressing on our
OL,10,Fcultural journey.
OL,12,F"A robust cultural audit, undertaken
OL,13,Fby an external company, has already
OL,14,Ftaken place at Mid and West Wales Fire
OL,15,Fand Rescue Service and as a result,
OL,16,Fthrough the formation of a Culture and
OL,17,FInclusion Board and Working Group, an
OL,18,Faction plan to make wide-ranging
OL,19,Fenhancements to our Service is
OL,20,Funderway, a process which has been
OL,21,Fwelcomed by Welsh Government.
